Organized for the students with an exemplary talent and interest for music, the music club has proven to be a platform for showcasing the sound and vibe of the college through music shows and an extra ordinary band.
With a noticeable number of talented members, the dance club has never failed to define the beat and rhythm of the college with its incredible dance crew. The beautification crew serves its purpose by furbishing the campus with never before seen ideas and innovations. The drama club was organized for the students with similar interests and passion to express themselves in various fields of drama, and the members have excelled themselves with constant practice and perfection. The media team has strived to express the heart and soul of our college to the world and thereby open a portal of opportunities for the students. With a wide range of innovative designs and creations, the design team holds the biggest number of extremely talented members to support its cause.
